{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "41dfb31f-ca3a-40bf-ab21-da3a88d6e74c", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/41dfb31f-ca3a-40bf-ab21-da3a88d6e74c@3.pkg/1772597502641/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597503205", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/41dfb31f-ca3a-40bf-ab21-da3a88d6e74c@3.pkg/1772597502641/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597503205"}, "identifier": "41dfb31f-ca3a-40bf-ab21-da3a88d6e74c", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>一审题干；二审设问；三审题肢。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>②④：分析题文，某小区解决“养老托幼”问题的过程中多方协商、集思广益，最后解决了问题，这体现了众人的事情由众人商量、群众合理诉求得以基本实现；故③④符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>①：根本政治制度是人民代表大会制度，题干并没有涉及；故①不符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>③：题干并没有涉及选举民主，不能其独特优势；故③说法错误；</p>\n\n<p>故本题选C。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（改编·2025湖南长沙中考真题）下面是某小区解决“养老托幼”问题的过程。该小区的做法好在（　　）</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"${ref-path}/edu/questions/image.png\">​</p>\n\n<p>①完善了我国的根本政治制度 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>②群众合理诉求得以基本实现</p>\n\n<p>③彰显了选举民主的独特优势</p>\n\n<p>④能让众人的事情由众人商量</p>\n", "title": "（改编·2025湖南长沙中考真题）下面是某小区解决“养老托幼”问题的过程。该小区的做法好在（　　）①完善了我国的根本政治制度         ②群众合理诉求得以基本实现③彰显了选举民主的独特优势④能让众人的事情由众人商量", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/41dfb31f-ca3a-40bf-ab21-da3a88d6e74c@3.pkg/item.json?v=1754819795339", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachmen